超震撼! 一起来看高铁列车的“夜生活”
9家动车运用所，满足日均320标准组检修任务
9 High-speed Train Maintenance Centers Put into Use in E China





China Railway Shanghai Group
9 Train Repair & Maintenance Centers

The Facilities Can Perform Repair and Maintenance of 

320 CRH Trains
on a Daily Basis

8 Units of Robots

at Night
The Vehicles
Will Run Safely
the Next Day

坐标：In East China




-------


The China Railway Shanghai Group Co. has recently launched 9 train repair and maintenance centers. The facilities can perform repair and maintenance of 320 CRH (China railway high-speed) trains on a daily basis. Meanwhile, 8 units of robots are employed to facilitate the repair and maintenance work. The work is carried out at night to ensure that the vehicles will be able to run safely the next day.
坐标：in east China



